item.title: CIPYD 317: Turkey Names and Tortoise Games
item.description:
Happy Hanukkah to you and yours! This week Alexis and Renee offer up a name for a Turkey BUT THERE ARE RULES! In CrickCrumBoat Tug (and possibly his very uncool mother) are humiliated AGAIN, while Cricket and Crumb inspire a new career endeavor! The Yourd Siblings and Max are here with a highly precision'd My Mutt Minute. And if that wasn't enough we've got a MIRACLE Christmas/Hanukkah story and a dog double winner!
